Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:40.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an4\c&H1A1A1A&\pos(205,475)}重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为了探索梅尔基涅海底遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,决定暂时离开爱尼森
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,始？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,梅尔基涅海底遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,应该就在这附近才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,自然风景不论在哪都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在日本的海边见过的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉很怀念 明明才过了半年不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟在这边每天都过得不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个应该是古卢恩攻略证明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,光都聚集起来了 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 真神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不错的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不像另外某个白痴解放者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊 很梦幻 我都有点感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 难怪一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,本来还想靠运气找到入口 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,水流真急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,又要被冲到其他地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,后方有什么东西在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,从缠绕的红黑色魔力来看肯定是魔物了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,正好试试我的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好 威力比之前更大了 改良成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 那里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是第五个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,五芒星的纹章和五个印记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,以及留存着光的项链
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠魔法想来这里可不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不能尽早察觉线索 魔力就不够用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,得感谢主人这艘船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看来好戏这才正式开场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是海底遗迹 根本就是个洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还好不是完全泡在水里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,交给月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,顶上好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,始 说实话有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,水也慢慢变深了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你也更轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,月大人 总感觉有点可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最近代替缪的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那以后就叫你小月月怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么对我这么刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不觉得太弱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太弱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 作为大迷宫的魔物而言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,希娅 别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我烫伤了 能帮我涂药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道现在什么状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,月大人和缇奥大姐双管齐下 应该没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,赐予圣净与治愈 天惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易有机会被摸胸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,始 这布丁好像能溶解魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,果然如此 刚刚我就奇怪火焰怎么被削弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看来连火焰里的魔力也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,终于有点大迷宫的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,月也去攻击 我负责防御
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,圣绝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么啊 整个空间都有魔物反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是大迷宫的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 不能让它无限再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,魔石在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 明明是透明的却看不见魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 它没有魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没有魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说它不是魔物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的魔眼石看来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它的身体全都是红黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就像布丁状的整个身体 都是一块魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,整个身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,整个空间都是同样的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定我们已经在它肚子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 该开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙真烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么办法对付它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,重整一下队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,地下还有空间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道通向什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还好 大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是小仓库级别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她们每个人我都给了宝物库
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她们自己会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,突然问这个干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你不去救月 而是救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为香织都快没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是月自己能想办法撑过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她还用眼神教训我了 让我来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你很信任她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那还用说 我们可是搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 你噶什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有空在这里垂头丧气 不如行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可是大迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是发了会儿呆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只能朝深处进发 继续探索了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,月她们也会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,算是船的乱葬岗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是战舰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 那艘最大的船感觉不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像客船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,始 看周围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是在做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我来防御 光绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这不仅是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有实体的攻击不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是带有魔力的攻击有用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 到底是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只要带有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,属性和效果一律都算攻击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我 把他杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就当是能直接触碰到的幻觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我有点慌了 不过现在没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老是道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是为了神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,埃希德大人万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,异教徒 死在我们的神面前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,香织 我们跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 到底怎样才能逃离这个恶心的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,应该有出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定哪艘船就是出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可有几百艘 怎么可能一艘艘去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得结束这场战争反而更快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就…结束这场战争？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,结束？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 总之先把他们都杀光怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这方案我喜欢 走吧 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,始 那到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,和这些废船有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,用幻术之类的把以前的战争再现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎加了一些改良 用来袭击大迷宫的挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定这就是这个大迷宫的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,主题？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,缇奥说过 每个大迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,应该都有解放者们准备的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那这里的主题…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,让人知晓发疯的神造成了什么惨剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,始 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别在意 我明白快被疯狂吞没时的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟我在奈落之底也曾差点被吞没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最后没被吞没 是因为月？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没遇到她 后果难以想象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望留住你的人和守护你的人 都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 我也不知道能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,连一个约定也没能遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,月真是强敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你动不动就道歉 苦笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,香织
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要跟我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,果然我还是碍事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得希娅怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,希娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,刚开始的时候 我对她很粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我只在乎月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望她能早日放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她一下生气一下开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有时还会哭鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此她也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不能使用魔法 只会使蛮力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她也从不会停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不会因自卑而屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没觉得自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里之后 你动不动就道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,连笑容都和以前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,香织 别低头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起头来看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我再说一次 我喜欢月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我会很重视其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但也改变不了月在我心中的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个事实只会让你觉得难受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果和月相比只会让你觉得自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,香织 那你最好还是离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今天必须把非常重要的事告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 畑山爱子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 来接我是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去和学生们吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你要去的地方是神山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是抛开主人自称为神的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能弹开我的魅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 不会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是颗优秀的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,得告诉其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:01.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:07.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:13.05,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.47,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:24.90,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:28.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.49,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:36.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:42.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:48.09,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:53.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.76,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:02.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆为虚空一场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破灭的希望　虚伪的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身体的伤口深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅是我　你也背负同样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得谁人原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕怀中相拥　徒留轮廓难辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘愿承伤不曾犹豫的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹒跚　忍痛离开你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}几步对错　令我身负百孔千疮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形单影只渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　谁人不曾拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
